<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/5553569-christine-koehne"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1436028082i/5553569._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/5553569-christine-koehne">Christine Koehne</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Yes, through Coffey's abilities. When William Wharton grabbed John Coffey's arm, he unknowingly showed what he did and how. When John told Paul he wan<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Yes, through Coffey's abilities. When William Wharton grabbed John Coffey's arm, he unknowingly showed what he did and how. When John told Paul he wanted to die he grabbed his hands and let him see Wharton's crime and told him he forgot that he saw Wharton drop the girls and run.<br /><br />Wharton never confessed even though Paul and his wife discussed it.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
