<div id="review_648882186" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/648882186" />
    <a title="Carol" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7668522-carol"><img alt="Carol" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1546364878p2/7668522.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/648882186?book_show_action=true">Jun 23, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Carol" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Carol" href="/user/show/7668522-carol">Carol</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback " href="/book/show/85424.The_Green_Mile">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=stephen-king">stephen-king</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=saw-the-movie">saw-the-movie</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=read-2015">read-2015</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7668522-carol?shelf=2015-super-favorites">2015-super-favorites</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer648882186" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11100175875910773601">When I decided to read <b>The Green Mile</b>, I was absolutely, positively 100% sure it would <i>never</i> measure up to the movie, and was I <i>ever</i> wrong.<p><i>All</i> of the characters <i>(including Mr. Jingles)</i> are so well drawn that you feel like you are experiencing their lives and feelings right along with them in Cold Mountain State Penitentiary-1932.</p><p>If I could rate this magical, unforgettable <i>(rip your heart out)</i> story more than 5 Stars, I would not hesitate to do so. What else can I say except.......&quot;Time takes it </p></span>
  <span id="freeText11100175875910773601" style="display:none">When I decided to read <b>The Green Mile</b>, I was absolutely, positively 100% sure it would <i>never</i> measure up to the movie, and was I <i>ever</i> wrong.<p><i>All</i> of the characters <i>(including Mr. Jingles)</i> are so well drawn that you feel like you are experiencing their lives and feelings right along with them in Cold Mountain State Penitentiary-1932.</p><p>If I could rate this magical, unforgettable <i>(rip your heart out)</i> story more than 5 Stars, I would not hesitate to do so. What else can I say except......."Time takes it all, whether you want it to or not".</p></span>
  <a data-text-id="11100175875910773601" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
